ions:"用户名是否存在" query_suggestions:"密码是否正确" query_suggestions:"用户名不存在" query_suggestions:"登陆成功" query_suggestions:"密码不正确！"}}} stream_id:"d273d476-916e-4f60-b60f-4a95a771cc4a"} messages:{message:{message_id:"bot-72d978f8-7e3d-4ec7-9278-9b94fe5e32e8" source:CHAT_MESSAGE_SOURCE_SYSTEM timestamp:{seconds:1700716086 nanos:365302416} conversation_id:"xsLjDbxXeb3aqItuF2aEJx5AdgOCsVm9" action:{generic:{text:"这段代码实现了登录功能。它接受一个`User`对象作为输入，并检查数据库中是否存在该用户名。如果用户名存在，它会检查提供的密码是否与数据库中的密码匹配。如果密码匹配，它将状态设置为\"success\"，消息设置为\"登录成功\"，并将用户信息传递给前端。如果密码不匹配，它将状态设置为\"error\"，消息设置为\"密码不正确！\"。如果用户名不存在，它也将状态设置为\"error\"，消息设置为\"用户名不存在\"。最后，它将结果以JSON字符串的形式返回。"} num_tokens:155 context_items:{absolute_path:"/home/lxw/Desktop/千锋教育/Java/day03_web/src/main/java/com/qfedu/make/dao/UserDao.java" workspace_paths:{workspace:"/home/lxw/Desktop/千锋教育/Java/day03_web" relative_path:"src/main/java/com/qfedu/make/dao/UserDao.java"} node_name:"UserDao" node_lineage:"com" node_lineage:"qfedu" node_lineage:"make" node_lineage:"dao" start_line:8 end_line:48 end_col:1 context_type:CODE_CONTEXT_TYPE_CLASS language:LANGUAGE_JAVA} context_items:{absolute_path:"/home/lxw/Desktop/千锋教育/Java/day03_web/src/main/java/com/qfedu/make/service/UserService.java" workspace_paths:{workspace:"/home/lxw/Desktop/千锋教育/Java/day03_web" relative_path:"src/main/java/com/qfedu/make/service/UserService.java"} node_name:"register" node_lineage:"com" node_lineage:"qfedu" node_lineage:"make" node_lineage:"service" node_lineage:"UserService" start_line:35 start_col:4 end_line:49 end_col:5 context_type:CODE_CONTEXT_TYPE_FUNCTION language:LANGUAGE_JAVA} context_items:{absolute_path:"/home/lxw/Desktop/千锋教育/Java/day03_web/src/main/java/com/qfedu/make/service/UserService.java" workspace_paths:{workspace:"/home/lxw/Desktop/千锋教育/Java/day03_web" relative_path:"src/main/java/com/qfedu/make/service/UserService.java"} node_name:"login" node_lineage:"com" node_lineage:"qfedu" node_lineage:"make" node_lineage:"service" node_lineage:"UserService" start_line:10 