您的描述，当点击除法按钮\"/\"时，它会将其拼接到`number1`上，而不是执行除法操作。\n\n这个问题可能是因为在按钮的点击事件处理程序中，对于除法按钮的处理与其他按钮不同。您可以尝试在除法按钮的`case`中添加一个额外的检查，以确保正确执行除法操作。例如，您可以修改代码如下：\n\n```javascript\ncase \"\\u00F7\":\n  operational = \"÷\";\n  break;\n```\n\n这将设置一个新的变量`operational`为\"÷\"，以便在后续的计算中正确执行除法操作。\n\n请尝试这个修改，并重新测试您的代码，看看是否能够解决问题。"} num_tokens:205 context_items:{absolute_path:"/home/lxw/Desktop/千锋教育/Java/LOL-html/js/calc.js" workspace_paths:{workspace:"/home/lxw/Desktop/千锋教育/Java/LOL-html" relative_path:"js/calc.js"} node_name:"onclick" start_line:16 start_col:2 end_line:98 end_col:4 context_type:CODE_CONTEXT_TYPE_FUNCTION language:LANGUAGE_JAVASCRIPT} context_items:{absolute_path:"/home/lxw/Desktop/千锋教育/Java/LOL-html/6.计算器.html" workspace_paths:{workspace:"/home/lxw/Desktop/千锋教育/Java/LOL-html" relative_path:"6.计算器.html"} node_name:"<!DOCTYPE html>" end_line:39 context_type:CODE_CONTEXT_TYPE_NAIVE_LINECHUNK language:LANGUAGE_HTML} context_items:{absolute_path:"/home/lxw/Desktop/千锋教育/Java/LOL-html/5.js的使用.html" workspace_paths:{workspace:"/home/lxw/Desktop/千锋教育/Java/LOL-html" relative_path:"5.js的使用.html"} node_name:"onclick" start_line:48 start_col:6 end_line:50 end_col:8 context_type:CODE_CONTEXT_TYPE_FUNCTION language:LANGUAGE_HTML} context_items:{absolute_path:"/home/lxw/Desktop/千锋教育/Java/LOL-html/css/lol-style.css" workspace_paths:{workspace:"/home/lxw/Desktop/千锋教育/Java/LOL-html" relative_path:"css/lol-style.css"} node_name:".zb5 > span," start_line:189 end_line:229 context_type:CODE_CONTEXT_TYPE_NAIVE_LINECHUNK language:LANGUAGE_CSS} context_items:{absolute_path:"/home/lxw/Desktop/千锋教育/Java/LOL-html/css/set-css.css" workspace_paths:{workspace:"/home/lxw/Desktop/千锋教育/Java/LOL-html" relative_path:"css/set-css.css"} node_name:"* {" end_line:84 context_type:CODE_CONTEXT_TYPE_NAIVE_LINECHUNK language:LANGUAGE_CSS}}} stream_id:"cb97ed5d-5761-4932-9a54-5bb6dec48852"} messages:{message:{message_id:"user-tISJkvBPp4p37fm2j7xI64gEMG7tSRPu" source:CHAT_MESSAGE_SOURCE_USER timestamp:{seconds:1701259709